          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Through her meticulous craftsmanship and cultural perspective, Graham creates clothing that serves as both statement and embrace, garments that transform not just appearance but experience. Each piece is sustainably made in Canada using locally sourced materials, reflecting her commitment to ethical production and environmental responsibility.</p>"
