        "text_ieUFRM": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Emmanuela Graham (EG) is an independent womenswear label living at the intersection of heritage and defiance. Rooted in cultural respect and engineered with industrial rigour, each piece is a quiet act of self-definition where structure meets fluidity, and tradition meets Innovation.</p><p>EG reimagines everyday wear by honouring the complexity of the modern woman: who she was taught to be, and who she is choosing to become. Through the discipline of pattern-making, the brand challenges conventional silhouettes and assumptions, crafting garments that are as intentional as they are versatile.</p><p>Designed with precision and purpose, EG empowers women to move through the world on their own terms, defining themselves through both function and form.</p>",
