            "text": "<p>At the heart of EG is Emmanuela, whose academic background in fashion and industrial design cultivated in the vibrant landscapes of Accra and Toronto shapes the brand's unique design philosophy. Her technical expertise and hands-on training in Accra enable her to explore the intersection of identity and form through pattern-making, crafting garments that are not only empowering, but also functional. <br/>Graham's work is marked by a sophisticated tension between tradition and innovation and this duality stands at the core of her philosophy. Through garments that are both functional and tasteful , she offers wearers a beautiful blend of freedom and power. </p>",
